{"tid":2402810,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今次先施馬家真係肉酸左啲","createTime":"2021-02-10T16:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T08:28:54.000Z","uid":357569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"023de82f657585434502029e63bf0061b5463593","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"【財華社訊】本地老牌百貨公司先施(00244-HK)去年5月獲中資內房股偉祿集團(01196-HK)以5億元提出全購，目前另外八項先決條件均未獲達成或宣佈達成，其中一項先決條件為要待保監局批准偉祿成為「先施人壽保險」及「先施保險置業」的「控權人」。<br />\n<br />\n偉祿集團公布，有關建議更改「先施人壽保險」及「先施保險置業」的「控權人」的申請已於上月26日提交予保險業監管局。<br />\n<br />\n先施上周四發公告，提到去年10月控股股東Win Dynamic曾訂立送贈契據，承諾向先施送贈其接納全購要約後所收取的2.6億元，惟Win Dynamic於上周三致函先施董事會，宣布契據無效，原因是當時曾受到「不當影響及威逼」。<br />\n<br />\nWin Dynamic由先施主席兼行政總裁馬景煊及非執行董事陳文衛分別持70%及30%權益，而Win Dynamic則持股先施50.42%。<br />\n<br />\n偉祿指出，注意到先施在契據公佈刊發後超過三個月才收到該信函，又指已向先施及Win Dynamic要求取得信函副本，以評估對交易造成任何影響，相信先施及先施董事會將採取一切必要合適措施，保障先施及先施股東的利益。<br />\n<br />\n偉祿將繼續專注於與達成交易的要約先決條件相關準備工作。"},{"pid":"54fddae443297d9d462622660eb2722ea565281e","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"估唔到先施都會淪落至此"},{"pid":"10035afda7e64d54c91bd7d829d3479f93bd99e7","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54fddae443297d9d462622660eb2722ea565281e","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"估唔到先施都會淪落至此"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"其實馬景煊揸旗咁柒耐都搞左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過業績越搞越差，分店越做就越少執得既都執鳩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n產品形象好老土又out都算<br />\n但呢獲野佢終於有成績改左，佢改走咗既老一輩生意人嘅良心道義同誠信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99785df2bffa87e15d0d69b747f7568e11510f5","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10035afda7e64d54c91bd7d829d3479f93bd99e7","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54fddae443297d9d462622660eb2722ea565281e","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"估唔到先施都會淪落至此"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"其實馬景煊揸旗咁柒耐都搞左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過業績越搞越差，分店越做就越少執得既都執鳩哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n產品形象好老土又out都算<br />\n但呢獲野佢終於有成績改左，佢改走咗既老一輩生意人嘅良心道義同誠信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:22:04.000Z","msg":"估佢唔到馬家呢啲名門望族既後人做生意都有無賴既一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2340b55339ae84cb536e5925fb46ebea4f938e0","tid":2402810,"uid":3659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:26:22.000Z","msg":"當年馬文輝直頭係真。港獨之父<br />\n行前幾十年，<br />\n如果唔係英國鳩縮，一早就學其他殖民地獨立咗啦<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5be8f716a4be5ba3701f0b49a6d792d0155c32","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a2340b55339ae84cb536e5925fb46ebea4f938e0","tid":2402810,"uid":3659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:26:22.000Z","msg":"當年馬文輝直頭係真。港獨之父<br />\n行前幾十年，<br />\n如果唔係英國鳩縮，一早就學其他殖民地獨立咗啦<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T19:49:55.000Z","msg":"黎到呢代家族生意又搞唔掂<br />\n出黎做生意重淪落到 出爾反爾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩撚完"},{"pid":"10f0a06ade7259989c6490d68847c3b1480c53bc","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"但其實成件事來龍去脈係點"},{"pid":"d31ed9e07ab1c1357281d62605b73e069ed82279","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"10f0a06ade7259989c6490d68847c3b1480c53bc","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"但其實成件事來龍去脈係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:20:19.000Z","msg":"自己睇睇咁曲折離奇的故事<br />\n<br />\n  事隔多月後，先施突於本月初公佈，收到Win Dynamic信函，宣佈於去年10月底簽定的送贈契據屬無效而且即時取消，原因是該契據是在受到不當影響及威迫，並且在概無獲給予獨立法律代表或適當意見情況下簽立，根據香港法例，該契據屬於一項遜值交易。<br />\n<br />\n  從了解所得，根據送贈契據，Win Dynamic去年10月已向先施不可撤回承諾，向先施送贈於其接納有關其持有的所有6.63億股先施股份要約後，Win Dynamic有權向要約人收取消售所得款項淨額，有關款項預期約達2.6億元。據早前契據，完成賣盤後，Win Dynamic有權向偉祿收取約2.6億元，並會無償轉贈予先施作營運資本。<br />\n<br />\n  然而先施於公佈中指出，董事會正在考慮該信函含意，並且不承認該契據屬無效或已被取消，亦不承認信函中所提述之任何其他事宜。聲明又提醒，該契據之存在與否並非要約之先決條件之一，董事會認為Win Dynamic據稱取消該契據，不會對要約人即將作出之要約造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n  如此重大交易，突然出現如此變化，難免令人感到兒戲，當中有何曲折，是否對偉祿存在不公，值得密切留意。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/241/20210211/912457/%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E9%AE%AE%E8%82%A1%E8%90%BD%E9%91%8A-%E5%81%89%E7%A5%BF%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%88%E6%96%BD%E7%AA%81%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F241%2F20210211%2F912457%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E8%2582%25A1%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%2591%258A-%25E5%2581%2589%25E7%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%2596%25BD%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2595%2585&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=a3ef44d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F241%2F20210211%2F912457%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E8%2582%25A1%25E8%2590%25BD%25E9%2591%258A-%25E5%2581%2589%25E7%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%2596%25BD%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2595%2585&h=d959adf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/241/20210211/912457/%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E9%AE%AE%E8%82%A1%E8%90%BD%E9%91%8A-%E5%81%89%E7%A5%BF%E8%B3%BC%E5%85%88%E6%96%BD%E7%AA%81%E7%94%9F%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%85</a>"},{"pid":"6b5d8bf1836e6272e09f765445369262ff7b7a0a","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">Win Dynamic去年10月已向先施不可撤回承諾，向先施送贈於其接納有關其持有的所有6.63億股先施股份要約後</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYLDAEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYLDAEP.png&h=83fac763&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁點解又會大大隻龜係到既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底係點被威逼呢"},{"pid":"cea1f5233d343da399bbee1325c9dacafc263ada","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b5d8bf1836e6272e09f765445369262ff7b7a0a","tid":2402810,"uid":351648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T18:51:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">Win Dynamic去年10月已向先施不可撤回承諾，向先施送贈於其接納有關其持有的所有6.63億股先施股份要約後</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYLDAEP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYLDAEP.png&h=83fac763&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁點解又會大大隻龜係到既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底係點被威逼呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T20:24:07.000Z","msg":"咁佢係主席 自然係署佢名 , 有咩出奇 奇係加在點解彈弓手姐"},{"pid":"9b0d609a9b134f06cec0332b1546de4c1a15695e","tid":2402810,"uid":52041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T22:19:58.000Z","msg":"本身個deal 似被逼，賣完股份d錢仲要送返比先施 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34855f90b98ebaa05436b5f0c458389c158e8862","tid":2402810,"uid":357569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b0d609a9b134f06cec0332b1546de4c1a15695e","tid":2402810,"uid":52041,"like":1,